short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A extension that help you create commands for the Beyond20 extension.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension helps you send media, such as images and gifs from D&D Beyond, through Beyond20 into Roll20. Read more here: https://github.com/Rasul-583/Roll20-Media-Sender/blob/main/README.md

v2 finally released! The extension actually works as intended now.
